                    <p><strong>Synopsis:</strong> "My Name is Stilton, Geronimo Stilton" is the first book in the Geronimo Stilton series, written by Italian author Elisabetta Dami. It follows the adventures of Geronimo Stilton, a mouse who works as a journalist and editor for the fictional newspaper, The Rodent's Gazette. The series combines humor, adventure, and education, targeting young readers.</p>
